### Running Tests

```bash
# Install development dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run all tests
pytest

# Run tests for specific module
pytest tests/test_formatter.py

# Run integration tests
pytest tests/test_integration.py

# Check code coverage
pytest --cov=talkie
```

